Package: pkgmkr
Title: Create an R Package with One Simple Function
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Shaurita", family = "Hutchins", email = "shaurita.d.hutchins@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7687-0059"))
Description: Simplifies the process of creating R packages by providing a single,
    straightforward function that handles package initialization, Git integration,
    license selection, README generation, and pkgdown site setup. Package creation
    can also be configured using YAML or JSON configuration files.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
